Curious bats, smirking Jack-o-Lanterns, witches on brooms and some costume fun! We are unleashing the scary quotient with a Halloween Night on 31 October 2019 with dinner & cocktails . A Spooktacular night awaits you at The Raviz Resort & Spa Ashtamudi!

Inclusions:
•Specially crafted menu & theme-related buffest dinner
•Halloween cocktails at INR 300 Net
•Black magic| Zombie Slime | Devil Eye| Vampire Back
•25% discount for Priviliz Card Members
